{"id": "1255515961654509568", "channel_id": "1255213639351406694", "type": 0, "author_id": "597345991632486406", "author_name": "whimsical_starfish_19845", "author_bot": false, "content": "", "timestamp": "2024-06-26T13:32:11.617000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}], "attachments": [{"id": "1255515961461706903", "filename": "56406.JPG", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 55498, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1255213639351406694/1255515961461706903/56406.JPG?ex=69cbccdb&is=69ca7b5b&hm=5b5b31e248df4491829d7103c50ec1d1258765ad8a5bf98ebb03a75b8e479d5d&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1255213639351406694", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "米粒活動收益計算", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174180524034637854"]}
{"id": "1255516535615914207", "channel_id": "1255213639351406694", "type": 0, "author_id": "597345991632486406", "author_name": "whimsical_starfish_19845", "author_bot": false, "content": "過往活動本共鳴開滿，收益倍率落在1.9~2.4倍之間，這次活動收益最高有3.08倍，應是對應了素材本的改動。\n\n須注意的是，除非很需要，不然通常不建議刷金卷本或購買金卷商店的素材，因此活動本實質上的收益會略少一些，但整體仍是賺的。", "timestamp": "2024-06-26T13:34:28.460000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-06-26T13:53:54.168000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1255213639351406694", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "米粒活動收益計算", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174180524034637854"]}
{"id": "1255517402238816266", "channel_id": "1255213639351406694", "type": 0, "author_id": "859055864899305472", "author_name": "foolkid_chang", "author_bot": false, "content": "金券商店的素材不買的話，不會缺嗎？活動給的很平均，如果不是平均練的話，某個界域的常常會缺 (我的血肉與混沌就比其他兩個界域少很多)", "timestamp": "2024-06-26T13:37:55.079000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1255213639351406694", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "米粒活動收益計算", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174180524034637854"]}
{"id": "1255517770641313843", "channel_id": "1255213639351406694", "type": 0, "author_id": "597345991632486406", "author_name": "whimsical_starfish_19845", "author_bot": false, "content": "以效益最大化的角度，建議在活動空檔去刷對應的素材本，比通常的金卷本收益更高。", "timestamp": "2024-06-26T13:39:22.913000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1255213639351406694", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "米粒活動收益計算", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174180524034637854"]}
{"id": "1255517826190544956", "channel_id": "1255213639351406694", "type": 0, "author_id": "597345991632486406", "author_name": "whimsical_starfish_19845", "author_bot": false, "content": "但金卷本如果有加成，就還是刷金卷本，然後可以買商店素材。", "timestamp": "2024-06-26T13:39:36.157000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1255213639351406694", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "米粒活動收益計算", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174180524034637854"]}
{"id": "1255518001491480596", "channel_id": "1255213639351406694", "type": 0, "author_id": "597345991632486406", "author_name": "whimsical_starfish_19845", "author_bot": false, "content": "對應的概念是，如果長期而言會缺金卷，需要在金卷本沒加成的時候刷的話，那就不建議購買商店的素材。", "timestamp": "2024-06-26T13:40:17.952000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1255213639351406694", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "米粒活動收益計算", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174180524034637854"]}
{"id": "1255518104738332805", "channel_id": "1255213639351406694", "type": 0, "author_id": "597345991632486406", "author_name": "whimsical_starfish_19845", "author_bot": false, "content": "還有一個隱含的概念是，玩久了，其實素材沒有太缺，除非界域單推，但金卷很缺。", "timestamp": "2024-06-26T13:40:42.568000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1255213639351406694", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "米粒活動收益計算", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174180524034637854"]}
{"id": "1255521136398041099", "channel_id": "1255213639351406694", "type": 0, "author_id": "597345991632486406", "author_name": "whimsical_starfish_19845", "author_bot": false, "content": "應該說，新手期，錢夠用，可以適當的買需要的素材，但到後面除非只玩單界域，打算要全部都開滿，不然不建議買。", "timestamp": "2024-06-26T13:52:45.372000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-06-26T13:53:05.252000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🫶", "emoji_id": null, "count": 3}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1255213639351406694", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "米粒活動收益計算", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174180524034637854"]}
{"id": "1255535633607426219", "channel_id": "1255213639351406694", "type": 0, "author_id": "1245664474275254362", "author_name": "9735fgyt", "author_bot": false, "content": "有没有大佬总结一下，笨笨看不懂\n就是刷金券很赚是吗？", "timestamp": "2024-06-26T14:50:21.776000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1255213639351406694", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "米粒活動收益計算", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174180524034637854"]}
{"id": "1255536706296348734", "channel_id": "1255213639351406694", "type": 19, "author_id": "597345991632486406", "author_name": "whimsical_starfish_19845", "author_bot": false, "content": "刷活動本 > 金卷本50%加成時 > 素材本 > 平常的金卷本\n商店素材在很缺的時候再買", "timestamp": "2024-06-26T14:54:37.525000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1245664474275254362"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1255535633607426219", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1255213639351406694", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "米粒活動收益計算", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174180524034637854"]}
{"id": "1255536850685132850", "channel_id": "1255213639351406694", "type": 0, "author_id": "597345991632486406", "author_name": "whimsical_starfish_19845", "author_bot": false, "content": "密契本看需求，可以適當的刷。", "timestamp": "2024-06-26T14:55:11.950000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 4}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1255213639351406694", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "米粒活動收益計算", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174180524034637854"]}
